  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Crossroads is a cozy visual novel experience where you assume the role of a bartender, listening to the customers and serving their drinks. 4 new customers need your help to change their fate and guide them to a better path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 unique characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 in-game days of gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple dialogue options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introducing: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valerian - The fish out of water</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras/a5b94c4e48809d138692ad286a41b78a.avif?t=1734470508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras_big/a5b94c4e48809d138692ad286a41b78a.avif?t=1734470508 width=800 height=704 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Orik - The jaded veteran</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras/537a1896a6ea1449ed9f35f4c3ae51a1.avif?t=1734470508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras_big/537a1896a6ea1449ed9f35f4c3ae51a1.avif?t=1734470508 width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jormun - The rebellious playboy Prince</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras/bf861f60f9e36f7d516f65665052b930.avif?t=1734470508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras_big/bf861f60f9e36f7d516f65665052b930.avif?t=1734470508 width=800 height=777 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kit - The budding musician</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras/1ba047e0f758f84f557f400209bb2993.avif?t=1734470508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras_big/1ba047e0f758f84f557f400209bb2993.avif?t=1734470508 width=800 height=707 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Crossroads is a cozy visual novel experience where you assume the role of a bartender, listening to the customers and serving their drinks. 4 new customers need your help to change their fate and guide them to a better path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 unique characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 in-game days of gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple dialogue options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introducing: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valerian - The fish out of water</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras/a5b94c4e48809d138692ad286a41b78a.avif?t=1734470508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras_big/a5b94c4e48809d138692ad286a41b78a.avif?t=1734470508 width=800 height=704 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Orik - The jaded veteran</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras/537a1896a6ea1449ed9f35f4c3ae51a1.avif?t=1734470508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras_big/537a1896a6ea1449ed9f35f4c3ae51a1.avif?t=1734470508 width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jormun - The rebellious playboy Prince</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350820/extras/bf861f60f9e36f7d516f65665052b930.avif?t=1734470508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai